{
  "stem": "10588.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Finally one said, you might as well tell her, because that's where we're all going to go.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she pointed to the smoke, which I don't, didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I thought maybe somebody has a factory there or something-- the smoke that was coming from the gas chambers, from the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she said, this is where our loved ones are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's where we're all going to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And at that point, if I could have died, it would have been welcome.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But you know, I remember when I was a little girl, my father and mother took me to a funeral [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we were there-- and I told you that I always noticed everything and wanted to know why.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I noticed that at the gate were some graves.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then we walked quite a distance, and there were a lot of graves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And those were separate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked my father, [NON-ENGLISH], Daddy, why is this grave separate?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, this is people who committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "According to the Jewish law, this is an offense to God and to the parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he mentioned-- he said it's like spitting God and your parents in the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it's not allowed, no matter what, to, to commit suicide.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in the despair, I remembered this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I cannot commit suicide because that's, that's spitting my parents.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were so good to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave the life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I prayed, dear God, take me, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[SOBBING] That was-- the pain was just tearing my heart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As I was sitting in the worst circumstances and crying, and all of a sudden I could give up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't care at that time about anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
